# Extraction-derived 3D model assets (LEGO Creator: Knights' Kingdom) --
# regenerate locally from your own game install via
# resources/model_files/convert_warehouse.mjs, convert_bricks.mjs, and
# copy_obj_assets.mjs. Matches resources/model_files/'s existing "don't
# commit extracted game assets" policy. Hand-authored assets (Archer,
# map1.glb, etc.) are NOT covered by these patterns and stay tracked.
src/Components/MainMenuStack/StartStack/MainGameStack/MainGame/ComponentTop/Bucket/BucketBottom/BucketBottomResourceStack/**/*.glb
public/workshop/bricks/*.glb
public/models/**/*.obj
public/models/**/*.mtl
public/models/textures/
